text: Migdalel Ruiz (born 3 Marzo 1983) is a Mexican volleyball player. She played at the 2002 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, 2002 Women's Pan- American Volleyball Cup, 2003 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2006 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, 2007 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2007 Women's NORCECA Volleyball Championship, and 2008 Women's Pan- American Volleyball Cup. She played for Guanajuato and Universidad Autónoma de Nuevo León's women's volleyball team. == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican volleyball players
